## 审稿报告格式

必须先逐章审稿，再综合审稿。不要只读整篇 `paper.tex` 后凭印象写总评。

### 逐章审稿产物

先读取 `drafts/paper_state.json` 和 `drafts/sections/*.tex`。对每个章节分别写：

- `drafts/review_rounds/round_{{ round }}_sections/abstract.md`
- `drafts/review_rounds/round_{{ round }}_sections/introduction.md`
- `drafts/review_rounds/round_{{ round }}_sections/related_work.md`
- `drafts/review_rounds/round_{{ round }}_sections/methodology.md`
- `drafts/review_rounds/round_{{ round }}_sections/experiments.md`
- `drafts/review_rounds/round_{{ round }}_sections/analysis.md`
- `drafts/review_rounds/round_{{ round }}_sections/conclusion.md`

每个逐章审稿文件至少包含：

```markdown
# Section Review: <section> (Round {{ round }})

## Section Purpose Check
[该章是否完成它在 outline / paper_state 中的职责]

## Evidence And Number Check
[数字、引用、图表是否可追溯；没有数字/引用的章节说明原因]

## Logic And Writing Issues
[本章内部逻辑、术语、过渡、overclaim 问题]

## CDR Alignment Check
[本章是否履行 CDR 职责；problem_frame/design_rationale/contribution_type/evaluation_mode/boundary_conditions 是否与正文证据一致]

## Alignment Matrix Check
[本章是否兑现它负责的 internal alignment lane；是否存在缺失、错误、无证据锚点或暴露内部编号的段落]

## Writing Craft Check
[本章是否违反 craft_audit 或 section craft：流水账、过度 claim、无效 citation key、独立 limitations 等]

## Actionable Fixes
- [High/Medium/Low] [可定位的修改建议]
```

